name: Thats Crazy
description: Alright, fam, get ready to vibe with the craziest meme token on Solana—"That’s Crazy"! Inspired by that iconic “wide-eyed cat” meme and the classic “Crazy” moment, this isn’t just a token; it’s a whole mood. We’re bringing together internet culture, humor, and crypto innovation into one wild ride. Whether you’re here for the memes, the community, or just wanna be part of something totally out there, "That’s Crazy" is your new home.
